title: The new 2020 catalogs are available online
body:
The pdf files of the ORTEANEXT 2020 catalogs are available for download.

Here are the links:

[ORTEA Voltage stabilizers](https://www.ortea.it/en/download-catalogues/)

[ORTEA LV Transformers](https://www.ortea.it/en/download-catalogues/)

[ORTEA SAG compensators](https://www.ortea.it/en/categorie_prodotti/sag-compensator-en/)

[ICAR Power factor correction systems](https://icar.ortea.com/en/download/)

[ICAR Active harmonic filters](https://icar.ortea.com/en/download/)
